membership:
Currently, its member organisation, as founding partners together with Fundación ONCE are: Association des Paralysés de France (APF), Kynnys ry in Finland, and Rytmus in the Czech Republic. &#xd;
&#xd;
Since September 2013, the network has incorporated six Associated Members from different European countries: queraum. cultural &amp; social research - Austria; FIRAH (International Foundation of Applied Disability Research) - France; University of Akureyri - Iceland;  Inclusion Ireland - Ireland; Association RENINCO - Romania; Centre for Studies on Inclusive Education UK.

